Class GameData

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.saving.GameData
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
ClientGameData
public class GameData extends Object implements Serializable
GameData allows to store and share information regarding a game (with no information regarding the game phase)
